@prefix : <https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix xml: <http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@base <https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#> .

<https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                           owl:versionIRI :sdc2-v1.0.0 ;
                                           owl:imports <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/cco-imports#2026-05-29> ,
                                                       <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/pato-imports#2026-05-27> ,
                                                       <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/pmdco-imports#2026-07-20> ,
                                                       <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/ro-imports#2026-05-29> ,
                                                       <http://ClimOO/climoo/climoo-sdc2/imports/sdc-ontology-imports/sdc-ontology-gdc-imports#2026-04-08> ,
                                                       <https://www.w3id.org/sco/sco-b#v1.1.0/sco-b> ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> "Giorgio A. Ubbiali" ,
                                                                                  "Ludger Jansen" ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Giorgio A. Ubbiali" ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> """ClimOO Ontology is a reference ontology, modeling plastics, (micro-)plastic pollution, climate change, and their interrelation, with a primary focus on agricultural systems. The ClimOO Ontology is structured in a suite of nested ontological modules.The SDC2 module forks the Sustainable Development and Climate (SDC) Ontology, updating the proposed models. The SDC2 module centers on climate and climate change, especially with regard to environmental features and related interconnections. Emphasis is also dedicated to relevant policies.

SDC ontology: https://github.com/hbabaie1/Sustainable-Development-and-Climate-SDC-ontology"""@en ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "ClimOO Ontology - ClimOO-SDC2 module"@en ;
                                           rdfs:comment """Currently, ClimOO-SDC2 focuses on the climate and climate change of the planet Earth. Nevertheless, it maintains a sufficiently flexible structure to accommodate and implement models concerning other planets.

According to relevant literature, the current representation leverages knowledge on climate and climate change, primarily referring to present and past climate trends, while climate change impacts are primarily addressed in terms of present and future effects."""@en ,
                                                        """The SDC Ontology provides a relevant model of climate and climate change, primarily with a focus on Sustainable Development Goals (Davarpanah et al., 2023). Despite its relevance, the SDC Onto model appears undermaintained and presents several shortcomings, including:
• Inconsistent hierarchy root.
• Absence of natural language definitions.
• Reusage of PATO representations that violate the BFO model, such as those concerning process properties, or that are inaccurate, such as those concerning increased and decreased dependent continuants.
• Misleadingness of certain classes.
• Inadequate axiomatization of certain classes.
For more details, see here (coming soon).

Thus, we forked SDC Onto to develop a novel version, named ClimOO-SDC2. ClimOO-SDC2 is the module of the ClimOO Ontology dedicated to climate change. ClimOO-SDC2 focuses on environmental features and related interconnections modeled in SDC Onto. ClimOO-SDC2 offers an active reference hub that addresses SDC Onto's shortcomings, while integrating the SDC Onto model into the ClimOO Ontology. ClimOO-SDC2 extends SCO, aligning the SDC Onto model with primary existing BFO-compliant sustainability ontologies. We intend ClimOO-SDC2 as an initial starting point to establish a unique BFO-compliant representation of climate and climate change. 

To construct ClimOO-SDC2, we proceed as follows (focus on OWL classes; we applied the same approach concerning the other OWL building blocks).
• If the class was not relevant, we did not import it.
• If the class was relevant and adequate, we directly imported it.
• If the class was relevant but inadequately axiomatized, we created a corresponding class that supports appropriate axioms but maintains the local identifier of the original SDC Onto class. We opted for this solution to offer a direct strategy of reference to the original version from which SDC2 has been forked. In the future, alternative, possibly more robust, strategies can be implemented. Exceptions: Given their centrality in the model, the following class has been supplied with ClimOO local identifiers and annotated towards original SDC Onto classes:
   • climate
   • climate change
   • (atmospheric) weather
   • climate system process
   • climate system component 
• If the class, despite axiomatization, was misleading, we did not import it, and we created adequate class(es) as needed. We supplied it with a ClimOO local identifier.
When revising classes, we complied with BFO and OBO-Foundry best practices.

All SDC2 building blocks support the following namespace to ensure appropriate identification and fairness: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#

Bibliography
Davarpanah, A., Babaie, H., & Dhakal, N. (2023). Semantic modeling of climate change impacts on the implementation of the U.N. sustainable development goals related to poverty, hunger, water, and energy. Earth Sci. Inf., 16(1), 929–943."""@en ;
                                           owl:versionInfo "2026-05-15"@en ,
                                                           "V1.0.0."@en ;
                                           <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> """Repository: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/repo
Documentation webpage: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/docs"""@en ,
                                                                                      "The most recent version of this file is available on GitHub at the following link: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2."@en .

#################################################################
#    Annotation properties
#################################################################

###  http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#minQualifiedCardinality
owl:minQualifiedCardinality rdf:type owl:AnnotationProperty .


#################################################################
#    Object Properties
#################################################################

###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/process_starts
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/process_starts> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


#################################################################
#    Classes
#################################################################

###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/Amount
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/Amount> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We envision discussions with subject matter experts and implementations concerning this class as related subclasses, as the term \"amount\" is quite ambiguous; for instance, it is not clear whether this class may refer to portions or the size of portions."""@en .


###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/NaturalProcess
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/NaturalProcess> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We include this class to comply with the original intended meaning of subclasses included from SDC Onto. We envision discussions with matter experts to deal with the distinction between natural and artificial features.

We currently comply with the original SDC Onto model concerning the included subclasses, seen as referring solely to natural processes. Implementations may expand coverage of these classes"""@en .


###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/Vulnerability
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/Vulnerability> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
Implementations are needed to align this representation with additional existing models, such as those proposed by COVER, ResiliOnt, and SuMSO.
See:
https://github.com/unibz-core/value-and-risk-ontology 
https://github.com/pedropaulofb/resiliont/tree/main 
https://w3id.org/sumso/repo"""@en .


###  https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000001
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000001> rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
For reasons of practicality, we did not subsume other ClimOO-SDC2 classes with respect to this class. We did not incorporate disjointness axioms to allow reclassification in such a manner. Implementations will deal with such an aspect, as needed."""@en .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Adaptive_Capacity
:Adaptive_Capacity rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:subClassOf :Capacity ;
                   rdfs:label "adaptive capacity"@en ;
                   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Adaptive_Capacity_to_Climate-related_Hazards_and_Natural_Disasters
:Adaptive_Capacity_to_Climate-related_Hazards_and_Natural_Disasters rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                    rdfs:subClassOf :Adaptive_Capacity ;
                                                                    rdfs:label "adaptive capacity to climate-related hazards and natural disasters"@en ;
                                                                    <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Affordability
:Affordability rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000016> ;
               rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
These classes required further implementations."""@en ;
               rdfs:label "affordability"@en ;
               <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Afforestaton
:Afforestaton rdf:type owl:Class ;
              rdfs:subClassOf :Land_Physical_Process ;
              rdfs:label "afforestation"@en ;
              <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Amount_of_River_Discharge
:Amount_of_River_Discharge rdf:type owl:Class ;
                           rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/Amount> ,
                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> ;
                                             owl:someValuesFrom :River
                                           ] ;
                           rdfs:label "amount of river discharge"@en ;
                           <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Arctic_Warming
:Arctic_Warming rdf:type owl:Class ;
                rdfs:subClassOf :Ocean_Physical_Process ,
                                :Warming ;
                rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
In compliance with the original model, we maintained this class as a subclass of the “ocean physical process” class.
To discuss whether the hierarchical root position may require revisions."""@en ;
                rdfs:label "arctic warming"@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Argon
:Argon rdf:type owl:Class ;
       rdfs:subClassOf :Gas ;
       rdfs:label "portion of argon"@en ;
       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Aridity
:Aridity rdf:type owl:Class ;
         rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> ;
         rdfs:label "aridity"@en ;
         <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atlantic_Meridional_Overtuning_Circulation
:Atlantic_Meridional_Overtuning_Circulation rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                            rdfs:subClassOf :Ocean_Circulation ;
                                            rdfs:label "atlantic meridional overtuning circulation"@en ;
                                            <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Change
:Atmospheric_Change rdf:type owl:Class ;
                    rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000305 ;
                    rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We excluded the upper-level class “change in climate system” as misinformative with respect to BFO representation of change and processes. We reclassified these classes as a subclass of the climate system process class https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304. We plan to discuss with subject matter experts to revise the model, implementing the current representation of changes and processes in the climate system. 
See https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Change_in_Climate_System and https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304"""@en ;
                    rdfs:label "atmospheric change"@en ;
                    <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Circulation
:Atmospheric_Circulation rdf:type owl:Class ;
                         rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000320 ;
                         rdfs:label "atmospheric circulation"@en ;
                         <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Component
:Atmospheric_Component rdf:type owl:Class ;
                       rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000024> ,
                                       [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         owl:unionOf ( [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                         owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002577>
                                                                       <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000006>
                                                                     )
                                                       ]
                                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                                         owl:someValuesFrom [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                              owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002577>
                                                                                            <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000006>
                                                                                          )
                                                                            ]
                                                       ]
                                                     )
                                       ] ,
                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000110> ;
                                         owl:someValuesFrom :Gas
                                       ] ,
                                       [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                         owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000177> ;
                                         owl:someValuesFrom :atmosphere
                                       ] ;
                       rdfs:label "atmospheric component" ;
                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Evaporative_Demand
:Atmospheric_Evaporative_Demand rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                rdfs:subClassOf :Demand ;
                                rdfs:label "atmospheric evaporative demand"@en ;
                                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Oxygen
:Atmospheric_Oxygen rdf:type owl:Class ;
                    rdfs:subClassOf :Oxygen ,
                                    [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                      owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                      owl:someValuesFrom :atmosphere
                                    ] ;
                    rdfs:label "portion of atmospheric oxygen"@en ;
                    <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Water_Demand
:Atmospheric_Water_Demand rdf:type owl:Class ;
                          rdfs:subClassOf :Demand ;
                          rdfs:label "atmospheric water demand"@en ;
                          <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Atmospheric_Water_Vapor
:Atmospheric_Water_Vapor rdf:type owl:Class ;
                         rdfs:subClassOf :Water_Vapor ,
                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                           owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                           owl:someValuesFrom :atmosphere
                                         ] ;
                         rdfs:label "portion of atmospheric water vapor"@en ;
                         <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Availability
:Availability rdf:type owl:Class ;
              rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> ;
              rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
Implementations will supply definitions to subclasses that require them."""@en ;
              rdfs:label "availability"@en ;
              <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Biodiversity
:Biodiversity rdf:type owl:Class ;
              rdfs:subClassOf :Diversity ;
              rdfs:label "biodiversity"@en ;
              <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Biosphere
:Biosphere rdf:type owl:Class ;
           rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000024> ,
                           [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             owl:unionOf ( [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                             owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002577>
                                                           <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000006>
                                                         )
                                           ]
                                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                             owl:someValuesFrom [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                  owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002577>
                                                                                <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000006>
                                                                              )
                                                                ]
                                           ]
                                         )
                           ] ,
                           [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                             owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                             owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000298
                           ] ;
           rdfs:label "portion of biosphere"@en ;
           rdfs:seeAlso "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01000817" ;
           <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Biospheric_Change
:Biospheric_Change rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000304 ;
                   rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We excluded the upper-level class “change in climate system” as misinformative with respect to BFO representation of change and processes. We reclassified these classes as a subclass of the climate system process class https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304. We plan to discuss with subject matter experts to revise the model, implementing the current representation of changes and processes in the climate system. 
See https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Change_in_Climate_System and https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304"""@en ;
                   rdfs:label "biospheric change"@en ;
                   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#CO
:CO rdf:type owl:Class ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Short-lived_Gas ;
    <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> "potion of CO"@en ;
    rdfs:label "portion of carbon monoxide"@en ;
    <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#CO2_Sink
:CO2_Sink rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:subClassOf :Sink ,
                          [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                            owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000174> ;
                            owl:someValuesFrom :Carbon_Dioxide
                          ] ;
          rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontoloy comment:
We did not include original subclasses, as those classes should be modeled by reclassifying ocean and land classes as CO2 sinks via axiomatization if needed.

http://www.semanticweb.org/Davarpanah-Babaie/ontologies/2021/9/ClimateOnSDG1267#Global_Land_CO2_Sink 
http://www.semanticweb.org/Davarpanah-Babaie/ontologies/2021/9/ClimateOnSDG1267#Global_Ocean_CO2_Sink"""@en ;
          rdfs:label "CO2 sink material entity"@en ;
          <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Capacity
:Capacity rdf:type owl:Class ;
          rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000019> ;
          rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
We envision discussions with subject matter experts and implementations concerning this class as related subclasses."""@en ;
          rdfs:label "capacity"@en ;
          <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Management
:Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Management rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                   rdfs:subClassOf :Capacity ;
                                                   rdfs:label "capacity for effective climate-related management"@en ;
                                                   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Planning
:Capacity_for_Effective_Climate-related_Planning rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                 rdfs:subClassOf :Capacity ;
                                                 rdfs:label "capacity for effective climate-related planning"@en ;
                                                 <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Carbon_Dioxide
:Carbon_Dioxide rdf:type owl:Class ;
                rdfs:subClassOf :Well-mixed_Greenhouse_Gas ;
                <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> "CO2"@en ;
                rdfs:label "portion of carbon dioxide"@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Carbon_Dioxide_Removal_on_Land
:Carbon_Dioxide_Removal_on_Land rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000304 ,
                                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                  owl:someValuesFrom :Biodiversity
                                                ] ,
                                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                  owl:someValuesFrom :Carbon_Dioxide
                                                ] ,
                                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                  owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000352
                                                ] ,
                                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                  owl:someValuesFrom :Soil_Carbon_Content
                                                ] ,
                                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000057> ;
                                                  owl:someValuesFrom :Water_Quantity
                                                ] ;
                                rdfs:label "carbon dioxide removal on land"@en ;
                                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


