                rdfs:seeAlso "http://www.semanticweb.org/Davarpanah-Babaie/ontologies/2021/9/ClimateOnSDG1267#Flood and subclasses."@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A process that leads to a partial or complete inundation of normally dry land areas, temporary or for a long period of time, due to the overflow of inland and/or tidal waters, and/or the unusual and rapid accumulation or runoff of surface waters from a water source."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/adaptedFrom> "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500002"@en ;
