                                  owl:someValuesFrom :Water
                                ] ,
                                [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                  owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002234> ;
                                  owl:someValuesFrom :ClimOO_0000329
                                ] ;
                rdfs:comment "To further discuss with subject matter experts."@en ;
                rdfs:label "water supplying process"@en ;
                rdfs:seeAlso """http://www.semanticweb.org/Davarpanah-Babaie/ontologies/2021/9/ClimateOnSDG1267#Supply_Role
http://www.semanticweb.org/Davarpanah-Babaie/ontologies/2021/9/ClimateOnSDG1267#Water_Supply and subclasses."""@en ;
                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A process that results in provisioning water to an entity of reference. Usually, this terminology is used with respect to provisioning water to populations, communities, and individuals, or alternatively, to geographical areas and sites."@en ;
                <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


