###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Damming
:Damming rdf:type owl:Class ;
         rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000304 ;
         rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment:
The original model seems primarily to refer to this class and subclasses for human-driven phenomena. However, the terminology used and the presence of a specific “Human-induced Greenhouse Gas Emission” class seem to indicate a broader applicability. We included these classes as having a broader applicability beyond human-driven phenomena, and created specific human-focused classes. Implementation may follow."""@en ,
                      """ClimOO Ontology comment:
this class requires implementations to clarify the intended meaning."""@en ;
         rdfs:label "damming"@en ;
         <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


