###  https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Geospheric_Change
:Geospheric_Change rdf:type owl:Class ;
                   rdfs:subClassOf :ClimOO_0000304 ;
                   rdfs:comment """ClimOO Ontology comment: 
We excluded the upper-level class “change in climate system” as misinformative with respect to BFO representation of change and processes. We reclassified these classes as a subclass of the climate system process class https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304. We plan to discuss with subject matter experts to revise the model, implementing the current representation of changes and processes in the climate system. 

See https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Change_in_Climate_System and https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#ClimOO_0000304"""@en ;
                   rdfs:label "geospheric change"@en ;
                   <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


