                                 """ClimOO ontology comment:
SDC Onto includes both this class and the class “change in the water cycle”. From the provided documentation, it is not totally clear the distinction between the two. We did not import the later and its subclasses. Implementations will deal with these classes. See
https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-sdc2#Change_in_the_Water_Cycle and subclasses."""@en ;
